285
00:15:14,844 --> 00:15:16,139
as a family, after all.

286
00:15:16,164 --> 00:15:17,437
It would be good for us

287
00:15:17,453 --> 00:15:18,812
to socialize occasionally.

288
00:15:19,164 --> 00:15:21,203
I'm glad you think that way.

289
00:15:22,133 --> 00:15:23,133
Speaking of which,

290
00:15:23,219 --> 00:15:24,992
Ranchaun told me today that

291
00:15:25,017 --> 00:15:28,273
you sent a servant to look for Malai.

292
00:15:28,602 --> 00:15:30,203
Did you two make up already?

293
00:15:31,503 --> 00:15:32,651
A husband and wife quarreling

294
00:15:32,676 --> 00:15:33,582
for too long isn't good.

295
00:15:33,606 --> 00:15:34,660
You should have

296
00:15:34,692 --> 00:15:37,496
informed me about Malai's whereabouts.

297
00:15:37,942 --> 00:15:39,543
I had to search for her for a long time.

298
00:15:41,801 --> 00:15:42,921
It's my fault.

299
00:15:43,395 --> 00:15:45,152
My preoccupation with work

300
00:15:45,629 --> 00:15:46,949
made me neglect Malai.

301
00:15:47,371 --> 00:15:48,722
No matter what,

302
00:15:48,785 --> 00:15:50,949
Malai is the wife favored by Father.

303
00:15:51,215 --> 00:15:52,925
Now that it has come to this,

304
00:15:52,949 --> 00:15:55,129
do not neglect the finances

305
00:15:55,154 --> 00:15:57,824
that Father has allocated for her.

306
00:16:00,215 --> 00:16:02,371
If Malai knows that you are concerned,

307
00:16:02,395 --> 00:16:04,075
she would be pleased.

308
00:16:39,738 --> 00:16:41,079
I implore you, Ms. Malai.

309
00:16:41,103 --> 00:16:42,774
Please grant me another chance

310
00:16:42,799 --> 00:16:44,470
to prove myself to you, Ms. Malai.

311
00:16:46,385 --> 00:16:48,573
Dech, please don't do this.

312
00:16:49,105 --> 00:16:50,308
No,

313
00:16:50,333 --> 00:16:52,035
if you refuse to forgive me,

314
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,660
I'll stay like this.

315
00:16:54,394 --> 00:16:55,245
Enough, Dech!

316
00:17:01,169 --> 00:17:02,849
If you want me to forgive you,

317
00:17:03,740 --> 00:17:05,091
you have to abandon

318
00:17:05,116 --> 00:17:06,319
everything and stay with me.

319
00:17:07,231 --> 00:17:09,840
I'm willing to follow you everywhere,

320
00:17:10,278 --> 00:17:11,535
be it heaven

321
00:17:12,286 --> 00:17:13,418
or hell,

322
00:17:13,715 --> 00:17:15,934
I'll never abandon Ms. Malai ever again.

323
00:17:48,622 --> 00:17:49,965
Ms. Ranchaun and Count Phichit

324
00:17:49,989 --> 00:17:51,051
went out for dinner,

325
00:17:51,076 --> 00:17:52,097
and they shouldn't have

326
00:17:52,122 --> 00:17:53,254
returned so soon.

327
00:18:58,468 --> 00:19:02,140
No, my lord!

328
00:19:02,327 --> 00:19:07,234
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

329
00:19:07,327 --> 00:19:12,335
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

330
00:20:08,793 --> 00:20:09,793
Dech!

331
00:20:20,827 --> 00:20:22,162
Where did Ms. Malai go?

332
00:20:23,858 --> 00:20:24,858
Dech!

333
00:20:26,748 --> 00:20:28,131
Dech!

334
00:20:28,670 --> 00:20:30,006
What's happening?

335
00:20:30,163 --> 00:20:31,498
Why did you come here?

336
00:20:32,116 --> 00:20:33,873
Don't ask right now, Ms. Malai.

337
00:20:34,084 --> 00:20:35,021
Just know that you

338
00:20:35,069 --> 00:20:36,170
can't stay here anymore.

339
00:20:36,195 --> 00:20:37,578
Dech!

340
00:20:38,444 --> 00:20:39,827
- Dech!
- Fueang!

341
00:20:40,163 --> 00:20:41,843
How did you get here, Fueang?

342
00:20:41,873 --> 00:20:42,873
Ms. Malai....

343
00:20:44,663 --> 00:20:45,732
The viscount has sent

344
00:20:45,741 --> 00:20:47,029
someone to kill you.

345
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:49,428
You have to escape with Dech right now,

346
00:20:49,453 --> 00:20:51,100
or else there's no way you will survive.

347
00:20:51,569 --> 00:20:53,217
Kill me?

348
00:20:53,545 --> 00:20:55,021
How did you find out about this?

349
00:20:57,155 --> 00:20:58,905
We have to take back our baby!

350
00:20:59,241 --> 00:21:00,256
I don't know what

351
00:21:00,272 --> 00:21:01,686
the viscount plans to do with him.

352
00:21:01,710 --> 00:21:03,241
Hurry up and go!

353
00:21:10,749 --> 00:21:12,194
Kam, take it.

354
00:21:13,347 --> 00:21:14,823
Why are you giving it to me?

355
00:21:14,848 --> 00:21:15,934
For killing Malai at

356
00:21:15,959 --> 00:21:17,410
Count Phichit's house, Kam.

357
00:21:29,294 --> 00:21:30,294
Ms. Malai.

358
00:21:30,319 --> 00:21:32,295
Be strong, Ms. Malai.

359
00:21:36,139 --> 00:21:37,678
I never thought the viscount

360
00:21:37,718 --> 00:21:39,287
could be this malicious.

361
00:21:40,538 --> 00:21:41,967
Ms. Malai,

362
00:21:42,850 --> 00:21:44,303
hurry and escape, ma'am.

363
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,412
Kam might have found out

364
00:21:46,421 --> 00:21:47,748
that you weren't in your room,

365
00:21:48,827 --> 00:21:50,627
and could be on the way here.

366
00:21:51,889 --> 00:21:54,717
Fueang is right. Let's go quickly.

367
00:21:55,303 --> 00:21:56,983
But where do we escape to, Dech?

368
00:21:57,460 --> 00:21:59,014
The viscount's residence in Hua Hin.

369
00:21:59,796 --> 00:22:01,803
But that place belongs to the viscount.

370
00:22:01,828 --> 00:22:03,092
Won't he

371
00:22:03,117 --> 00:22:04,797
easily find us there?

372
00:22:04,866 --> 00:22:06,334
The most dangerous place,

373
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:08,467
is also the safest place, Ms. Malai.

374
00:22:12,858 --> 00:22:13,858
Fueang,

375
00:22:14,441 --> 00:22:15,855
you should come with us.

376
00:22:15,918 --> 00:22:16,792
No,

377
00:22:16,894 --> 00:22:18,628
I've decided to stay here.

378
00:22:18,949 --> 00:22:20,363
I'll be a useless burden

379
00:22:20,387 --> 00:22:21,827
if I go with you.

380
00:22:22,315 --> 00:22:24,620
Hurry, take Ms. Malai and escape.

381
00:22:25,387 --> 00:22:27,214
- But...
- No buts.

382
00:22:27,660 --> 00:22:29,340
Don't try to force me.

383
00:22:35,177 --> 00:22:37,777
When you change your mind, please come.

384
00:22:39,052 --> 00:22:40,317
Thank you,

385
00:22:40,490 --> 00:22:42,458
I'll follow you when I change my mind.

386
00:22:42,638 --> 00:22:44,067
For now, hurry up and go.

387
00:22:44,091 --> 00:22:45,211
Please, ma'am.

388
00:22:45,513 --> 00:22:46,755
I'll get going, Fueang.

389
00:22:47,208 --> 00:22:48,231
Hurry up and go.

390
00:22:48,786 --> 00:22:49,879
Let us go, Ms. Malai.

391
00:22:52,146 --> 00:22:54,692
Please go, ma'am.

392
00:23:01,438 --> 00:23:03,219
I'm can only be your little sister.

393
00:23:05,735 --> 00:23:06,937
If I go,

394
00:23:07,727 --> 00:23:10,453
it'll only bring me heartache.

395
00:23:11,946 --> 00:23:13,725
I hope you'll be happy

396
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,498
with the one you love.

397
00:23:18,899 --> 00:23:20,781
Please be happy for me.

398
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:42,331
You can't even handle this simple task!

399
00:23:42,394 --> 00:23:43,573
- Useless!
- I apologize!

400
00:23:43,738 --> 00:23:44,932
I apologize, my lord.

401
00:23:45,448 --> 00:23:46,815
When I arrived,

402
00:23:46,894 --> 00:23:48,370
but Ms. Malai wasn't there.

403
00:23:48,542 --> 00:23:50,198
I don't know where she went.

404
00:23:51,558 --> 00:23:52,776
Don't make excuses!

405
00:23:53,066 --> 00:23:54,815
You let her escape, didn't you?

406
00:23:54,847 --> 00:23:56,198
That's not true, my lord.

407
00:23:56,323 --> 00:23:58,104
My child's life is at stake,

408
00:23:58,221 --> 00:24:00,518
I dare not disobey your orders, my lord.

409
00:24:00,736 --> 00:24:02,948
- Kam!
- My lord!

410
00:24:09,261 --> 00:24:10,354
It's true, my lord.

411
00:24:11,478 --> 00:24:12,633
How can the servants dare

412
00:24:12,658 --> 00:24:13,846
to defy your orders, my lord?

413
00:24:13,870 --> 00:24:16,175
You have our little one too,

414
00:24:17,808 --> 00:24:19,393
please forgive us.

415
00:24:19,579 --> 00:24:20,774
Please, my lord.

416
00:24:20,799 --> 00:24:21,776
Please forgive us.

417
00:24:21,801 --> 00:24:23,081
Please, my lord.

418
00:24:26,649 --> 00:24:27,586
My lord.

419
00:24:27,595 --> 00:24:28,595
What now?

420
00:24:28,829 --> 00:24:30,196
Dech is not in his room, my lord.

421
00:24:30,221 --> 00:24:31,282
We searched everywhere

422
00:24:31,306 --> 00:24:32,358
and couldn't find him.

423
00:24:32,383 --> 00:24:34,101
I'm afraid he might have escaped.

424
00:24:37,372 --> 00:24:38,824
Evil woman and vile man!

425
00:24:40,481 --> 00:24:41,996
Both of them eloped for sure!

426
00:24:44,223 --> 00:24:45,254
Where is Fueang?

427
00:24:45,536 --> 00:24:46,504
Fueang is working in

428
00:24:46,520 --> 00:24:47,676
the kitchen, my lord.

429
00:24:48,278 --> 00:24:49,278
Good!

430
00:24:55,608 --> 00:24:56,648
Little one...

431
00:25:05,729 --> 00:25:06,931
Which guy are you planning

432
00:25:06,948 --> 00:25:08,056
to use it on, my lord?

433
00:25:08,182 --> 00:25:09,619
That's none of your business.

434
00:25:09,994 --> 00:25:13,470
Geez, I didn't mean to pry, my lord.

435
00:25:14,143 --> 00:25:15,635
I was just concerned that you might

436
00:25:15,658 --> 00:25:17,689
force yourself on someone.

437
00:25:20,658 --> 00:25:23,252
Are there no men who desire you now?

438
00:25:25,549 --> 00:25:26,970
I'll never need to

439
00:25:27,267 --> 00:25:29,478
resort to desperate measures like you.

440
00:25:30,158 --> 00:25:31,494
Use your time to become

441
00:25:31,526 --> 00:25:33,127
a suitable mother for the child.

442
00:25:33,252 --> 00:25:34,830
Don't interfere in my affairs.

443
00:25:57,882 --> 00:25:58,882
Oh.

444
00:26:00,280 --> 00:26:01,280
My lord.

445
00:26:02,921 --> 00:26:04,975
My lord, why have you come here?

446
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,428
I think you know why.

447
00:26:09,023 --> 00:26:10,725
Do you know where Dech ran away to?

448
00:26:11,218 --> 00:26:12,749
Did Dech really run away, my lord?

449
00:26:12,774 --> 00:26:14,054
I was not aware.

450
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:15,538
Don't pretend to be innocent

451
00:26:15,546 --> 00:26:16,491
with me, Fueang.

452
00:26:16,499 --> 00:26:17,983
I did no such thing, my lord.

453
00:26:18,008 --> 00:26:19,928
I truly don't know where Dech went.

454
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:23,076
Fine.

455
00:26:23,537 --> 00:26:24,959
You choose to be stubborn

456
00:26:24,967 --> 00:26:26,115
with me, Fueang.

457
00:26:50,358 --> 00:26:51,897
What are you doing, my lord?

458
00:26:55,749 --> 00:26:57,124
I know that you and Dech love

459
00:26:57,155 --> 00:26:58,514
each other like siblings.

460
00:26:58,835 --> 00:27:00,436
You tell each other everything.

461
00:27:02,092 --> 00:27:03,288
Where is he?

462
00:27:10,601 --> 00:27:12,616
This is your last chance to tell me

463
00:27:12,687 --> 00:27:13,887
where Dech went.

464
00:27:15,218 --> 00:27:16,350
I don't know, my lord.

465
00:27:17,749 --> 00:27:18,811
You're being stubborn!

466
00:27:18,836 --> 00:27:20,069
Asking nicely didn't work.

467
00:27:20,507 --> 00:27:21,631
Now you'll find out

468
00:27:21,913 --> 00:27:22,928
what consequences

469
00:27:22,953 --> 00:27:24,233
being stubborn with me entails!

470
00:27:24,241 --> 00:27:26,944
Please let go, my lord! It hurts!

471
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:28,100
Please let go!

472
00:27:35,788 --> 00:27:37,569
No, my lord!

473
00:27:37,694 --> 00:27:39,811
My lord, release me!

474
00:27:40,976 --> 00:27:41,976
Not telling me?

475
00:27:41,991 --> 00:27:43,499
No, my lord!

476
00:27:45,530 --> 00:27:46,530
My lord!

477
00:27:46,569 --> 00:27:47,929
Please let me go!

478
00:27:48,499 --> 00:27:50,280
Let go, my lord!

479
00:27:53,038 --> 00:27:55,061
You're just the beginning, Fueang!

480
00:27:55,351 --> 00:27:56,553
Anything he loves,

481
00:27:56,601 --> 00:27:58,077
anything important to him,

482
00:27:58,101 --> 00:27:59,163
I will destroy it all.

483
00:27:59,187 --> 00:28:00,413
Absolute scum!

484
00:28:02,265 --> 00:28:07,273
