00:28:23,655 --> 00:28:24,855
Thank you, Dech.

489
00:28:24,882 --> 00:28:26,592
It's a commoner outfit,

490
00:28:26,608 --> 00:28:28,358
I'm uncertain if it will fit you.

491
00:28:29,679 --> 00:28:30,780
I can wear it just fine.

492
00:28:30,804 --> 00:28:32,004
No need to try.

493
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,889
You can leave it on the table.

494
00:28:33,921 --> 00:28:35,397
I cleaned up a bit earlier.

495
00:28:40,615 --> 00:28:41,748
Cleaning up alone must

496
00:28:41,795 --> 00:28:42,990
be tiring, Ms. Malai.

497
00:28:43,381 --> 00:28:44,741
Please let me take over.

498
00:28:45,435 --> 00:28:48,452
I'm almost done, you don't need to.

499
00:28:49,124 --> 00:28:50,483
But I want to help, really.

500
00:28:51,225 --> 00:28:52,834
I said you don't have to.

501
00:28:53,405 --> 00:28:55,092
Please attend to something else.

502
00:28:57,247 --> 00:28:58,411
But I wish to be with

503
00:28:58,436 --> 00:28:59,787
Ms. Malai all the time.

504
00:29:01,858 --> 00:29:02,858
Excuses.

505
00:29:03,780 --> 00:29:05,670
There are other tasks you could

506
00:29:05,686 --> 00:29:07,725
be attending to in this large house

507
00:29:07,733 --> 00:29:10,045
instead of sticking close to me.

508
00:29:14,238 --> 00:29:16,066
It's not like I've had many chances

509
00:29:16,091 --> 00:29:18,113
to be alone with you like this.

510
00:29:23,811 --> 00:29:25,473
May I stay with you for a while and

511
00:29:25,489 --> 00:29:26,855
find delight in your company?

512
00:29:30,192 --> 00:29:31,192
Geez, Dech.

513
00:29:32,684 --> 00:29:33,871
You're becoming more daring.

514
00:29:35,473 --> 00:29:37,465
♪ Beautiful love ♪

515
00:29:37,489 --> 00:29:40,262
I find happiness in being with you.

516
00:29:40,287 --> 00:29:41,933
♪ When you find it ♪

517
00:29:41,958 --> 00:29:44,301
Are you displeased with my actions?

518
00:29:44,315 --> 00:29:46,080
♪ You try to embrace it ♪

519
00:29:48,151 --> 00:29:50,963
♪ You dedicate to it ♪

520
00:29:51,425 --> 00:29:54,132
♪ You give it your all ♪

521
00:29:54,893 --> 00:29:59,740
♪ So that it lasts forever ♪

522
00:30:00,058 --> 00:30:03,331
♪ But sometimes
it turns into darkness ♪

523
00:30:03,356 --> 00:30:06,399
♪ If you love so much
that it blinds you ♪

524
00:30:06,761 --> 00:30:12,448
♪ Beauty can turn into pain ♪

525
00:30:18,651 --> 00:30:20,171
How do I look, Dech?

526
00:30:20,972 --> 00:30:22,198
Absolutely beautiful.

527
00:30:24,253 --> 00:30:25,293
Are you sure?

528
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:26,955
Without a doubt, my Ms. Malai.

529
00:30:26,972 --> 00:30:28,518
looks beautiful and elegant

530
00:30:28,543 --> 00:30:29,846
in whatever she wears.

531
00:30:31,292 --> 00:30:32,534
Oh, you and your sweet talk.

532
00:30:33,104 --> 00:30:34,541
I'm speaking the truth.

533
00:30:35,222 --> 00:30:36,198
For me,

534
00:30:36,776 --> 00:30:38,182
Ms. Malai is always the most beautiful.

535
00:30:40,643 --> 00:30:41,948
Thank you, Dech.

536
00:30:44,776 --> 00:30:46,260
When I get to live like this,

537
00:30:46,799 --> 00:30:48,409
hearing you say things like this

538
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:51,846
I can't help but feel like

539
00:30:52,690 --> 00:30:54,143
I'm living in a dream.

540
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:58,221
You're not dreaming, Ms. Malai.

541
00:30:58,909 --> 00:31:00,393
I'm here with you.

542
00:31:06,354 --> 00:31:07,713
That's what I'm afraid of.

543
00:31:08,987 --> 00:31:11,924
Sometimes I feel like my life is cursed.

544
00:31:14,401 --> 00:31:16,518
Whenever there's a moment of happiness,

545
00:31:16,534 --> 00:31:17,971
I often encounter sorrows

546
00:31:18,276 --> 00:31:19,956
beyond imagination.

547
00:31:21,636 --> 00:31:22,698
So...

548
00:31:30,953 --> 00:31:32,632
Please stop speaking, Ms. Malai.

549
00:31:33,945 --> 00:31:35,171
You're not cursed.

550
00:31:36,969 --> 00:31:38,726
We both deserve to live together

551
00:31:38,751 --> 00:31:40,111
until we're old.

552
00:31:44,491 --> 00:31:46,171
That would be nice.

553
00:31:46,695 --> 00:31:48,054
It will be like that,

554
00:31:49,875 --> 00:31:51,335
Because I will do everything

555
00:31:51,969 --> 00:31:53,539
to make you the happiest woman

556
00:31:53,547 --> 00:31:54,667
in the world.

557
00:31:58,773 --> 00:31:59,773
Dech!

558
00:32:01,117 --> 00:32:02,117
Dech!

559
00:32:07,156 --> 00:32:08,156
Dech!

560
00:32:10,227 --> 00:32:11,227
Dech!

561
00:32:11,438 --> 00:32:12,320
Let go!

562
00:32:12,336 --> 00:32:13,336
I refuse.

563
00:32:14,430 --> 00:32:15,140
Dech!

564
00:32:15,165 --> 00:32:16,165
I refuse.

565
00:32:56,905 --> 00:32:59,585
(Hua Hin Residence)

566
00:33:05,022 --> 00:33:06,264
Dech, how brave of you.

567
00:33:07,233 --> 00:33:08,834
You dare to escape to my vacation home!

568
00:33:10,468 --> 00:33:11,631
Someone like you

569
00:33:13,014 --> 00:33:14,733
will never have a peaceful death!

570
00:33:17,772 --> 00:33:18,772
Hey.

571
00:33:20,279 --> 00:33:21,794
Save your words to curse Dech.

572
00:33:22,116 --> 00:33:24,280
If it weren't for him cheating on me,

573
00:33:24,694 --> 00:33:26,678
I wouldn't even think of touching you

574
00:33:26,803 --> 00:33:28,537
and dirting my own hands.

575
00:33:30,468 --> 00:33:31,639
In fact,

576
00:33:31,866 --> 00:33:33,717
if you knew how to use your brain

577
00:33:33,742 --> 00:33:35,694
and be loyal to someone,

578
00:33:36,014 --> 00:33:37,451
your stubbornness might

579
00:33:38,186 --> 00:33:40,248
have some good use, Fueang.

580
00:33:41,522 --> 00:33:43,381
You're only good at harming others,

581
00:33:43,483 --> 00:33:45,233
no foolish dogs would

582
00:33:45,258 --> 00:33:46,938
pledge loyalty to you!

583
00:33:49,936 --> 00:33:51,225
That's true.

584
00:33:51,905 --> 00:33:52,967
But my methods

585
00:33:54,069 --> 00:33:56,084
get results. Agree?

586
00:33:59,295 --> 00:34:00,295
Revolting!

587
00:34:01,499 --> 00:34:02,490
You can only resort

588
00:34:02,514 --> 00:34:03,631
to underhanded tricks!

589
00:34:03,656 --> 00:34:05,575
Self-serving bias!

590
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:06,912
Absolute scum!

591
00:34:11,326 --> 00:34:12,944
Dech betrayed me.

592
00:34:13,733 --> 00:34:14,990
Anything he loves,

593
00:34:15,757 --> 00:34:17,287
anything important to him,

594
00:34:17,538 --> 00:34:18,990
I will destroy it all.

595
00:34:19,015 --> 00:34:21,701
You're just the beginning, Fueang!

596
00:34:56,632 --> 00:35:00,759
No matter what, Dech
must come back to me!

597
00:35:01,335 --> 00:35:04,894
If you fail this time,
your child will be killed.

598
00:35:05,047 --> 00:35:09,968
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

599
00:35:09,976 --> 00:35:14,984
(House of the Dark Shadows
novel: Phakhinai, screenplay: Wannason)

600
00:35:16,449 --> 00:35:17,569
Go to this destination.

601
00:35:18,152 --> 00:35:20,003
This time, you must kill Malai,

602
00:35:20,035 --> 00:35:21,597
and then bring Dech back to me.

603
00:35:24,003 --> 00:35:25,003
But...

604
00:35:25,261 --> 00:35:26,941
Will Dech agree, my lord?

605
00:35:26,996 --> 00:35:28,019
Even if he refuses,

606
00:35:28,441 --> 00:35:29,722
you have to make him agree.

607
00:35:29,808 --> 00:35:30,737
No matter what,

608
00:35:30,753 --> 00:35:32,136
Dech must come back to me.

609
00:35:32,161 --> 00:35:33,339
Come and settle the score for

610
00:35:33,363 --> 00:35:34,409
what he has done to me.

611
00:35:35,246 --> 00:35:36,378
Understood, my lord.

612
00:35:36,894 --> 00:35:38,417
If you make another mistake,

613
00:35:38,543 --> 00:35:40,003
your child will die for sure.

614
00:35:40,668 --> 00:35:41,800
Understood, my lord.

615
00:35:46,893 --> 00:35:48,501
You can't escape from me, Dech!

616
00:36:18,684 --> 00:36:19,684
Uan.

617
00:36:20,052 --> 00:36:21,052
Fueang.

618
00:36:21,077 --> 00:36:22,077
Uan.

619
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:25,676
Please release me.

620
00:36:26,692 --> 00:36:28,067
I only brought food for you,

621
00:36:28,091 --> 00:36:29,559
following the viscount's orders.

622
00:36:30,677 --> 00:36:32,114
No need to follow the orders

623
00:36:32,130 --> 00:36:33,575
of scum like the viscount!

624
00:36:34,091 --> 00:36:35,325
Please let me go!

625
00:36:36,177 --> 00:36:37,177
Oh, Fueang,

626
00:36:37,802 --> 00:36:40,700
if I let you go, what will happen to me?

627
00:36:41,512 --> 00:36:43,231
My child is with the viscount.

628
00:36:43,450 --> 00:36:44,810
I can't help you.

629
00:36:45,177 --> 00:36:46,598
If you don't let me go,

630
00:36:47,872 --> 00:36:49,887
I won't be able to help Ms. Malai.

631
00:36:52,083 --> 00:36:53,996
Ms. Malai has been good to

632
00:36:54,021 --> 00:36:55,426
me and to you.

633
00:36:57,434 --> 00:36:59,082
I want to help Ms. Malai too,

634
00:36:59,286 --> 00:37:01,434
but I also have my child to think of.

635
00:37:01,442 --> 00:37:04,962
You know how cruel the viscount is.

636
00:37:05,364 --> 00:37:07,067
My child might die.

637
00:37:08,450 --> 00:37:09,450
Uan.

638
00:37:10,278 --> 00:37:12,345
Ms. Malai is a human being too.

639
00:37:15,273 --> 00:37:17,366
I apologize, but I truly can't help you.

640
00:37:17,834 --> 00:37:18,834
Uan!

641
00:37:19,132 --> 00:37:21,545
Uan!

642
00:37:35,263 --> 00:37:37,505
I'm sorry, Dech.

643
00:37:39,860 --> 00:37:41,060
I'm sorry.

644
00:38:01,168 --> 00:38:02,949
You seem so calm, my lord.

645
00:38:03,816 --> 00:38:05,222
So unlike one who orders

646
00:38:05,247 --> 00:38:07,019
his own man to kill his wife.

647
00:38:09,363 --> 00:38:10,355
What are you saying?

648
00:38:13,783 --> 00:38:14,783
Geez,

649
00:38:14,892 --> 00:38:16,790
don't feign ignorance, my lord.

650
00:38:17,454 --> 00:38:20,743
Didn't my lord send Kam to kill

651
00:38:20,759 --> 00:38:22,199
Ms. Malai and Dech?

652
00:38:24,220 --> 00:38:25,602
It's none of your business.

653
00:38:28,462 --> 00:38:31,009
How can it not be my business?

654
00:38:31,493 --> 00:38:32,649
After all,

655
00:38:34,712 --> 00:38:36,141
Dech is my husband too.

656
00:38:44,671 --> 00:38:46,311
Dech only followed my orders.

657
00:38:46,648 --> 00:38:47,999
He is not your husband.

658
00:38:48,093 --> 00:38:49,436
Don't meddle with Dech again,

659
00:38:49,453 --> 00:38:50,358
or

660
00:38:51,093 --> 00:38:52,538
you get a peaceful death.

661
00:39:08,742 --> 00:39:09,804
If I die,

662
00:39:10,867 --> 00:39:12,241
you won't survive either.

663
00:39:18,492 --> 00:39:19,843
Please step aside, I beg you.

664
00:39:19,859 --> 00:39:20,859
I refuse.

665
00:39:21,117 --> 00:39:22,265
If you're going to shoot,

666
00:39:22,290 --> 00:39:24,155
shoot me along with Ms. Malai.

667
00:39:24,179 --> 00:39:25,179
No!

668
00:39:27,686 --> 00:39:28,913
How rowdy.

669
00:39:29,749 --> 00:39:30,869
Hello, Father.

670
00:39:35,578 --> 00:39:37,085
I didn't do anything wrong!

671
00:39:37,234 --> 00:39:38,914
Why must you care about what

672
00:39:38,921 --> 00:39:40,975
those people are spouting

673
00:39:41,898 --> 00:39:43,311
when it's not the truth?

674
00:39:45,054 --> 00:39:46,382
Rerai!

675
00:40:00,634 --> 00:40:06,194
♪ Here's a heart
that's always faithful ♪

676
00:40:06,430 --> 00:40:10,554
♪ Ready to be given
to you for good ♪

677
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:17,994
♪ Here's a life
that's still being offered ♪

678
00:40:18,731 --> 00:40:22,248
♪ To you alone ♪

679
00:40:22,412 --> 00:40:28,218
♪ You might be unaware
and still wondering ♪

680
00:40:28,465 --> 00:40:34,498
♪ Why I'm willing to do
everything for you ♪

681
00:40:35,087 --> 00:40:37,538
♪ Whatever you want ♪

682
00:40:37,981 --> 00:40:42,625
♪ Everything I've done ♪

683
00:40:42,967 --> 00:40:45,250
♪ What's it for? ♪

684
00:40:45,290 --> 00:40:50,640
♪ I can't give you my reasons ♪

685
00:40:51,217 --> 00:40:56,635
♪ Love has its own reason ♪

686
00:40:57,000 --> 00:41:02,498
♪ I've only done
what my heart wants ♪

687
00:41:02,815 --> 00:41:08,578
♪ All you have to do
is accept my love ♪
